scheme PSeparation { I() -> set,A() -> (ManySortedSet of I()),P[set,set] } : (ex X being (ManySortedSet of I()) st (for i being set holds (i in I() implies (for e holds (e in ( X . i ) iff (e in ( A() . i ) & P[ i,e ]))))))
proof
